      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Hey newbie,\n\nYour first client is a kid named Jonathan. He is struggling
    with a big fear of being alone, and it shows up in his dreams as a dark forest
    with no clear path. Everything feels quiet and empty, which makes even small
    things feel scary. Your goal is to help him move through this space and learn
    that being alone does not always mean being unsafe.\n\nYou will find a campfire
    in the forest. This is his safe spot. Collect firewood to keep it burning while
    exploring and avoiding anything that feels threatening. The stronger the fire,
    the braver Jonathan becomes. \n\nTake your time, stay alert, and help him build
    the courage to keep going. \n\nGood luck! "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 14332c434199d405389a686126a1f137, type: 2}
